{"tid":2018422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢一刻打緊仗，走去玩曲線式唱紅打黑係極度不智。","createTime":"2020-05-15T15:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T16:44:13.000Z","uid":219007,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e39dd7d0753c679a0edc6ea6ca43f673565b117","tid":2018422,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"呢個時間係戰爭，無啦啦走去玩曲線根本害死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果香港係可以合法有槍，依一刻已經係內戰狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府軍vs 反政府同盟軍 街頭子彈橫飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過係香港無槍咁解，而無可否認嘅係，依一刻係打仗，對立非常分明。<br />\n<br />\n套用共產黨講法，呢個已經唔係人民內部矛盾，而係敵我矛盾，唔係你死就我亡。 試問有冇人會喺打仗嘅時刻喺戰場上面玩曲線扮敵人，國際戰線會唔會真心當真？？ <br />\n<br />\n玩得一次，到時候狼來了人哋會唔會再信你？<br />\n<br />\n當年真愛聯係佔領後既先玩，當時社會係完全平衡時空，政治時事議題根本冇乜人理，真愛聯先有價值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同呢個時候比根本兩個唔同時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc07eb523e3d73ee6b05dfe69d0223f9946e2f6c","tid":2018422,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"高質,推"},{"pid":"18f7dc50adf6891ba48a472710ca866af626ead0","tid":2018422,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"用下腦得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec04dfe1c03d289593025ce1b89776ccea5dea78","tid":2018422,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6116f565cd4849767e8947591870679fc738ea63","tid":2018422,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485e46f6e6fa82